text: Thalassicolla is a radiolarian genus reported in the Thalassicollidae. The genus contains bioluminescent species. It is a genus of solitary (not colonial) radiolarians. ==Species== The following species are recognized (incomplete list): * Thalassicolla nucleata Huxley, 1851 ==References== Category:Radiolarian genera Category:Bioluminescent radiolarians
title: Thalassicolla
